{"questionId":"22312757","questionHtml":"<p>Show that&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>attempt to use implicit differentiation&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mfenced><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><em>A1A1</em></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>A1</strong></em> for LHS and <em><strong>A1</strong></em> for RHS.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>attempt to expand brackets and collect <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></math> terms on the same side&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></msup><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></msup></math>&nbsp; &nbsp;OR&nbsp; &nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></msup><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></math>&nbsp; &nbsp;OR&nbsp; &nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></msup></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><em>A1</em></strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><em>AG</em></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><strong><em>[5 marks]</em></strong></p>","meta":{"questionId":"22312757","referenceCode":"24M.2.AHL.TZ1.11a","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Show that dydx=2x-ex+yex+y-2y.","paper":"2","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 5]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5 —Calculus","Topic 5 —Calculus","SL 5.6—Differentiating polynomials n E Q. Chain, product and quotient rules","Topic 5 —Calculus","AHL 5.14—Implicit functions, related rates, optimisation"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}